metadata.name: Frank Ape's Reese's Puffs
metadata.description: This is a hand-painted one of a kind piece on an official Travis Scott Reese's Puffs limited edition collectors box. Originally I was saving the box for my personal collection and then I decided to Frankify it. I painted the front of the box to morph Travis Scott into Frank Ape and each little puff is now a tiny Frank embryo jumping for joy out of the bowl. It is perfect for the ultimate Frank Ape and Travis Scott fan.
